  "scenes": [
    {"id":"scene_056_world3_start","worldId":"world3","title":"诸神的黄昏","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"我在坠落。\n\n不，准确地说，是在漂浮。\n\n周围是破碎的石块，金色的血液，还有...神的尸体？","background":"temple_ruins","characters":[],"bgm":"world3","nextSceneId":"scene_057_world3","effects":{"hiddenStats":{"chaos":10}}},
    {"id":"scene_057_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"洛恩","dialogue":"我落地了——或者说，我控制着自己落在了一块漂浮的岛屿上。\n\n这是一座神殿的废墟。巨大的石柱断裂，神像破碎，地面上流淌着金色的液体。\n\n神血。","background":"temple_ruins","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_058_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_058_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"米迦勒","dialogue":"「又一个来了。」\n\n一个虚弱的声音从身后传来。\n\n我转过身，看到一个长着翅膀的人——或者说，曾经长着翅膀。他的翅膀被撕裂，金色的血液从伤口流出。","background":"temple_ruins","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_059_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_059_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"洛恩","dialogue":"「你是谁？」我问。\n\n「我是米迦勒。」他说，「或者说，曾经是。」\n\n「最后一个天使，最后一个还活着的神。」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_060_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_060_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"米迦勒","dialogue":"「神...死了？」\n\n米迦勒苦笑：「诸神黄昏，三千年前就开始了。」\n\n「神族与人族的战争，持续了千年。最后...两败俱伤。」\n\n「神族几乎灭绝，人族...也付出了惨重的代价。」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_061_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_061_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"米迦勒等待着你的回应。你选择：","background":"temple_ruins","characters":["michael"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_030_a","text":"「为什么告诉我这些？」","nextSceneId":"scene_062_world3_a","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":8},"bonds":{"world3":5}}},{"id":"choice_030_b","text":"「我能做什么？」","nextSceneId":"scene_062_world3_b","effects":{"stats":{"courage":5,"compassion":5},"bonds":{"world3":8}}},{"id":"choice_030_c","text":"「这和我有什么关系？」","nextSceneId":"scene_062_world3_c","effects":{"stats":{"determination":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_062_world3_a","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"米迦勒","dialogue":"「因为你不一样。」米迦勒说，「你的灵魂...不属于这个世界。」\n\n「你是穿越者。你能做到我们做不到的事。」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_063_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_062_world3_b","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"米迦勒","dialogue":"「你能阻止『那个』。」米迦勒说，「阻止祂的苏醒。」\n\n「否则，所有世界...都会毁灭。」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_063_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_062_world3_c","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"米迦勒","dialogue":"米迦勒深深地看着你。\n\n「你以为这是巧合吗？」\n\n「为什么你偏偏来到这里，而不是其他世界？」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_063_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_063_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"米迦勒","dialogue":"「祂是谁？」\n\n米迦勒沉默了很久。\n\n「创造者。」他说，「也是毁灭者。」\n\n「所有世界的源头...也是所有世界的终结。」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_064_world3","dialogueVariants":[{"conditions":{"stats":{"wisdom":{"min":60}}},"text":"「祂是谁？」\n\n米迦勒惊讶地看着你：「你...已经猜到了，对吗？」\n\n「你的智慧超出了我的想象。」\n\n「没错，就是『创造者』。所有世界的源头...也是所有世界的终结。」"}],"extraLines":{"courage":"米迦勒说：「你的勇气让我想起了过去的自己。那时，我也相信能改变一切。」","compassion":"米迦勒的语气柔和了：「你心中有爱。这很好...因为只有爱能战胜恐惧。」","bond":"米迦勒看向远方：「{world}的人民...还在等待希望。」"}},
    {"id":"scene_064_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"米迦勒","dialogue":"「我不明白。」\n\n「你不需要明白。」米迦勒说，「你只需要知道...」\n\n「当你到达初始之境时，你会面临选择。」\n\n「选择毁灭...还是选择重生。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_065_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_065_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"米迦勒的身体开始消散。\n\n「时间不多了。」他说，「去吧...去初始之境。」\n\n「记住...你的选择，决定一切。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":["michael"],"nextSceneId":"scene_066_world3"},
    {"id":"scene_066_world3","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"米迦勒消失了。你独自一人站在神殿废墟上。你选择：","background":"temple_ruins","characters":[],"choices":[{"id":"choice_031_a","text":"【前往初始之境】立刻出发","nextSceneId":"scene_067_world3_journey","effects":{"stats":{"determination":10}}},{"id":"choice_031_b","text":"【探索神殿】先收集信息","nextSceneId":"scene_067_world3_explore","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10}}},{"id":"choice_031_c","text":"【祈祷】寻求神的指引","nextSceneId":"scene_067_world3_pray","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":10},"hiddenStats":{"chaos":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_067_world3_journey","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你展开翅膀——半神的翅膀，金色的羽毛在阳光下闪耀。\n\n你飞向天空，朝着那道紫色的裂隙前进。\n\n但途中，你感觉到了...某种存在。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_068_world3_encounter"},
    {"id":"scene_067_world3_explore","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你在神殿中搜索。\n\n在祭坛下，你发现了一块石碑，上面刻着古老的文字：\n\n「当神血染红大地，穿越者将降临...」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_068_world3_clue"},
    {"id":"scene_067_world3_pray","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你跪在破碎的神像前，闭上眼睛。\n\n没有回应。\n\n神已经死了。或者...他们只是不再倾听。","background":"temple_ruins","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_068_world3_silent"},
    {"id":"scene_068_world3_encounter","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"神秘存在","dialogue":"「停下，半神。」\n\n一个声音在你脑海中响起。\n\n「你不是第一个穿越者。也不会是最后一个。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_069_world3_mystery"},
    {"id":"scene_068_world3_clue","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"石碑继续写道：\n\n「他将携带众神的记忆，面对创造者的审判。」\n\n「选择吧：毁灭，或重生。」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_069_world3_prophecy"},
    {"id":"scene_068_world3_silent","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"就在你准备放弃时，神像的眼睛...闪烁了一下。\n\n一个微弱的声音：\n\n「去...神陨战场...那里有...答案...」","background":"temple_ruins","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_069_world3_godfall"},
    {"id":"scene_069_world3_mystery","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"这个存在是谁？你选择：","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"choices":[{"id":"choice_032_a","text":"「你是谁？」","nextSceneId":"scene_070_world3_voice","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5}}},{"id":"choice_032_b","text":"「你想干什么？」","nextSceneId":"scene_070_world3_threat","effects":{"stats":{"courage":5}}},{"id":"choice_032_c","text":"【无视】继续前进","nextSceneId":"scene_070_world3_ignore","effects":{"stats":{"determination":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_069_world3_prophecy","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"预言...你注定要面对创造者。\n\n但你不确定，这是命运，还是诅咒。\n\n你收起石碑，准备离开。","background":"temple_ruins","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_070_world3_journey"},
    {"id":"scene_069_world3_godfall","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"神陨战场。那是诸神最后战斗的地方。\n\n据说，那里仍然弥漫着神的力量。\n\n你展开翅膀，朝那个方向飞去。","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_070_world3_battlefield"},
    {"id":"scene_070_world3_voice","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"神秘存在","dialogue":"「我是...记忆。」\n\n「所有死去的神的记忆。」\n\n「现在，他们在你体内。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_071_world3_memory"},
    {"id":"scene_070_world3_threat","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"神秘存在","dialogue":"存在笑了。\n\n「我想帮你。」\n\n「但帮助的方式...可能不是你想的那样。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_071_world3_help"},
    {"id":"scene_070_world3_ignore","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你继续飞行。\n\n声音消失了。\n\n但你知道，它还在看着你。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_071_world3_silent"},
    {"id":"scene_070_world3_journey","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你离开神殿，踏上旅程。\n\n前方，是未知的命运。\n\n但你已经做好了准备。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_071_world3_travel"},
    {"id":"scene_070_world3_battlefield","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你来到了神陨战场。\n\n这里...依然能感受到神的力量。\n\n地面上，插满了破碎的神器。","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_071_world3_artifacts"},
    {"id":"scene_071_world3_memory","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"突然，无数记忆涌入你的脑海。\n\n你看到了：神的诞生，神的战争，神的陨落...\n\n还有...一个紫色的裂隙。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_072_world3_vision","effects":{"hiddenStats":{"chaos":10}}},
    {"id":"scene_071_world3_help","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"神秘存在","dialogue":"「听着。」\n\n「创造者即将苏醒。」\n\n「你必须在他完全苏醒之前...做出选择。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_072_world3_choice"},
    {"id":"scene_071_world3_silent","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你继续飞行。\n\n但心中总有一种感觉...\n\n你并不孤单。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_072_world3_feeling"},
    {"id":"scene_071_world3_travel","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你飞越破碎的大地。\n\n下方，是神战的遗迹。\n\n上方，是紫色的裂隙。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_072_world3_approach"},
    {"id":"scene_071_world3_artifacts","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"神器散落一地。你选择：","background":"godfall","characters":[],"choices":[{"id":"choice_033_a","text":"【拿起神剑】","nextSceneId":"scene_072_world3_sword","effects":{"stats":{"courage":15}}},{"id":"choice_033_b","text":"【拿起神盾】","nextSceneId":"scene_072_world3_shield","effects":{"stats":{"determination":15}}},{"id":"choice_033_c","text":"【不拿】保持纯净","nextSceneId":"scene_072_world3_pure","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10},"hiddenStats":{"corruption":-10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_072_world3_vision","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"洛恩","dialogue":"「那是...」\n\n你看到了裂隙的另一端。\n\n其他世界。其他勇者。\n\n「我们...都是碎片。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_073_world3_realize"},
    {"id":"scene_072_world3_choice","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"选择？什么选择？你问道。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"choices":[{"id":"choice_034_a","text":"「什么选择？」","nextSceneId":"scene_073_world3_explain","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5}}},{"id":"choice_034_b","text":"「我拒绝选择。」","nextSceneId":"scene_073_world3_refuse","effects":{"stats":{"determination":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_072_world3_feeling","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"这种感觉...很奇怪。\n\n像是有人在看着你，引导着你。\n\n但你不知道是谁。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_073_world3_mystery"},
    {"id":"scene_072_world3_approach","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你越来越接近裂隙。\n\n能感觉到它的力量在拉扯你。\n\n「这就是...初始之境的入口。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_073_world3_enter"},
    {"id":"scene_072_world3_sword","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你拿起了神剑。\n\n力量涌入你的身体。\n\n「这是...宙斯的雷霆之剑。」","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_073_world3_power"},
    {"id":"scene_072_world3_shield","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你拿起了神盾。\n\n雅典娜的庇护。\n\n「这将保护我面对最终的战斗。」","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_073_world3_defend"},
    {"id":"scene_072_world3_pure","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你没有触碰任何神器。\n\n「我的力量，来自内心。」\n\n你说。\n\n「不需要外物。」","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_073_world3_inner"},
    {"id":"scene_073_world3_realize","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你终于明白了。\n\n艾莉娅，K-7，你...\n\n都是创造者的碎片。\n\n「我们...本是一体。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_074_world3_unite"},
    {"id":"scene_073_world3_explain","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"神秘存在","dialogue":"「毁灭，还是重生。」\n\n「创造者将这两个选择放在你面前。」\n\n「而你，必须决定所有世界的命运。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_074_world3_destiny"},
    {"id":"scene_073_world3_refuse","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"神秘存在","dialogue":"存在沉默了。\n\n「拒绝选择...也是一种选择。」\n\n「但后果...你可能无法承受。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_074_world3_consequence"},
    {"id":"scene_073_world3_mystery","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你继续前进。\n\n mystery 依然存在。\n\n但现在，这不是最重要的。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_074_world3_focus"},
    {"id":"scene_073_world3_enter","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你踏入裂隙。\n\n身体被光芒包围。\n\n当你再次睁开眼...\n\n你站在了纯白的空间中。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_void"},
    {"id":"scene_073_world3_power","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"神剑与你融为一体。\n\n你感觉...前所未有的强大。\n\n「这就是...神的力量。」","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_074_world3_strong"},
    {"id":"scene_073_world3_defend","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"神盾融入你的手臂。\n\n防御力大幅提升。\n\n「这将保护我面对创造者。」","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_074_world3_protected"},
    {"id":"scene_073_world3_inner","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"没有神器，你反而感觉...\n\n更纯净。\n\n「我的力量，来自内心。」","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_074_world3_pure"},
    {"id":"scene_074_world3_unite","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你感受到了其他碎片。\n\n艾莉娅在永夜王国。\n\nK-7 在机械废土。\n\n林小满...在学园都市。\n\n「我们必须...汇聚。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_gather"},
    {"id":"scene_074_world3_destiny","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"命运的重担压在你肩上。你选择：","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"choices":[{"id":"choice_035_a","text":"「我接受。」","nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_accept","effects":{"stats":{"determination":15}}},{"id":"choice_035_b","text":"「我要找到第三条路。」","nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_third","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":15}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_074_world3_consequence","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"存在叹息。\n\n「那就让一切...自然发展吧。」\n\n「无论结果如何，都是你的选择。」","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_natural"},
    {"id":"scene_074_world3_focus","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你集中精神。\n\n现在最重要的是...\n\n面对创造者。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_focus"},
    {"id":"scene_074_world3_strong","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你感觉...无所不能。\n\n但你也知道...\n\n力量越大，责任越大。","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_responsibility"},
    {"id":"scene_074_world3_protected","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"有了神盾的保护。\n\n你更有信心面对创造者。\n\n「来吧。」","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_confident"},
    {"id":"scene_074_world3_pure","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"纯净的状态。\n\n没有外力的干扰。\n\n你的判断更清晰。","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_075_world3_clear"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_void","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"纯白。\n\n无边无际的纯白。\n\n你站在这片虚无之中，周围漂浮着无数...记忆碎片？","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_fragments"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_gather","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你尝试联系其他碎片。\n\n但没有回应。\n\n「他们...还没准备好。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_wait"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_accept","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你接受了命运。\n\n无论前方是什么...\n\n你都会面对。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_courage"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_third","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"第三条路...\n\n毁灭与重生之外...\n\n还有什么选择？","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_think"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_natural","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你选择顺其自然。\n\n但你知道...\n\n最终还是要面对。","background":"sky_rift","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_patience"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_focus","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你集中精神。\n\n前方，就是初始之境的核心。\n\n「准备好了。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_ready"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_responsibility","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"力量与责任。\n\n你明白了米迦勒的话。\n\n「我会...做出正确的选择。」","background":"godfall","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_wise"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_confident","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"带着信心，你继续前进。\n\n创造者...等着我。\n\n「我来了。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_approach"},
    {"id":"scene_075_world3_clear","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"清晰的思维。\n\n这是最宝贵的武器。\n\n「我准备好了。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_076_world3_mental"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_fragments","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你伸手触碰其中一个碎片。\n\n画面涌现——那是艾莉娅，在教堂中醒来。\n\n另一个碎片——K-7，在废墟中睁开眼睛。\n\n再一个——洛恩，在神殿中坠落。\n\n还有...林小满，在图书馆中做出选择。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_vision"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_wait","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你等待。\n\n在纯白的空间中，时间没有意义。\n\n你可以等...永远。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_eternity"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_courage","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"勇气。\n\n这是你最大的武器。\n\n「来吧，命运。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_brave"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_think","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你思考。\n\n毁灭与重生...\n\n也许...还有别的可能。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_idea"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_patience","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"耐心。\n\n有时候，等待也是选择。\n\n「我会等到...时机成熟。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_patient"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_ready","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"准备好了。\n\n无论前方是什么。\n\n「我来了。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_enter"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_wise","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"智慧与力量。\n\n这是完美的组合。\n\n「我会做出正确的选择。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_correct"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_approach","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你走向核心。\n\n那里，有一个身影在等待。\n\n「终于...」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_meet"},
    {"id":"scene_076_world3_mental","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"清晰的思维。\n\n这是你最强大的武器。\n\n「准备好了。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_077_world3_mental_ready"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_vision","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"？？？","dialogue":"「欢迎回来。」\n\n一个声音响起。\n\n我转过身，看到了...我自己？\n\n不，不完全一样。那个「我」的眼睛，是纯粹的金色。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_creator"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_eternity","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"永远...\n\n这个词现在有了意义。\n\n你不再焦急。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_calm"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_brave","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你勇敢地前进。\n\n没有什么能阻挡你。\n\n「来吧。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_fearless"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_idea","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"一个想法在你脑海中形成。\n\n也许...\n\n「我可以...」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_plan"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_patient","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你耐心等待。\n\n时机...会到来的。\n\n在那之前，你等待。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_waiting"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_enter","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你踏入核心区域。\n\n这里，一切都很安静。\n\n「有人在吗？」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_call"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_correct","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"正确的选择...\n\n什么是正确？\n\n你会找到的。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_search"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_meet","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"？？？","dialogue":"身影转过身。\n\n金色的眼睛看着你。\n\n「你终于来了。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_face"},
    {"id":"scene_077_world3_mental_ready","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"思维清晰。\n\n你准备好了面对一切。\n\n「来吧。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_mental_face"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_creator","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「我是谁？」我问。\n\n「你是『我』。」他说，「或者说，你是『我』的一部分。」\n\n「我是创造者，也是毁灭者。」\n\n「我是所有世界的源头，也是所有世界的终结。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_079_world3_why"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_calm","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"平静。\n\n你心中充满了平静。\n\n「我准备好了。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_creator"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_fearless","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"无所畏惧。\n\n这就是你的状态。\n\n「来吧。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_creator"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_plan","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"计划在你脑海中形成。\n\n也许...\n\n还有别的路。","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_creator"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_waiting","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"等待中，你思考。\n\n思考...\n\n「我明白了。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_creator"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_call","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「我在这里。」\n\n声音从四面八方传来。\n\n「我一直在这里。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_creator"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_search","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你寻找答案。\n\n在内心深处...\n\n「找到了。」","background":"void","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_078_world3_creator"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_face","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「我是谁？」我问。\n\n「你是『我』。」他说，「或者说，你是『我』的一部分。」\n\n「我是创造者，也是毁灭者。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_079_world3_why"},
    {"id":"scene_078_world3_mental_face","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「你终于来了。」\n\n金色的眼睛看着你。\n\n「我一直在等你。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_079_world3_why"},
    {"id":"scene_079_world3_why","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"洛恩","dialogue":"「为什么...要把自己分裂？」\n\n创造者沉默了很久。\n\n「因为痛苦。」他说，「创造带来的痛苦。」\n\n「我看着无数生命在我的世界中诞生、挣扎、死去。」\n\n「我无法承受...所以我选择了逃避。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_080_world3_escape"},
    {"id":"scene_080_world3_escape","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「我把自己的意识分裂成无数碎片，散落在各个世界。」\n\n「我想体验凡人的生活，想理解...存在的意义。」\n\n「但现在，碎片正在汇聚。」\n\n「我即将苏醒。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_081_world3_choice"},
    {"id":"scene_081_world3_choice","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"创造者等待着你的回应。你选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_036_a","text":"「阻止他。」","nextSceneId":"scene_082_world3_stop","effects":{"stats":{"courage":10,"determination":10},"hiddenStats":{"corruption":10}}},{"id":"choice_036_b","text":"「接受他。」","nextSceneId":"scene_082_world3_accept","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":10,"wisdom":5},"hiddenStats":{"chaos":10}}},{"id":"choice_036_c","text":"「问他一个问题。」","nextSceneId":"scene_082_world3_ask","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":15}}},{"id":"choice_036_d","text":"【毁灭】「毁灭吧，所有世界。」","nextSceneId":"scene_082_world3_destroy","conditions":{"hiddenStats":{"corruption":{"min":50}}},"fallbackSceneId":null,"effects":{"hiddenStats":{"corruption":20}}},{"id":"choice_036_e","text":"【守护】「为了所有世界的人！」","nextSceneId":"scene_082_world3_protect","conditions":{"bonds":{"world1":{"min":30}}},"fallbackSceneId":null,"effects":{"stats":{"determination":15,"compassion":10},"bonds":{"world1":10,"world2":10,"world3":10,"world4":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_082_world3_stop","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"洛恩","dialogue":"「我不会让你苏醒。」\n\n「如果你苏醒，所有世界都会毁灭，对吗？」\n\n创造者点点头：「是的。我的苏醒，意味着所有碎片的回归。」\n\n「意味着...所有世界的终结。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_083_world3_confront"},
    {"id":"scene_082_world3_accept","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"洛恩","dialogue":"「那就苏醒吧。」\n\n「如果这是注定要发生的，我不会阻止。」\n\n创造者看着我，眼神复杂。\n\n「你...不害怕吗？」\n\n「害怕。但我更害怕...逃避。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_083_world3_merge"},
    {"id":"scene_082_world3_ask","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"洛恩","dialogue":"「我有一个问题。」\n\n「如果所有世界都毁灭了...那些生命，那些故事，还有什么意义？」\n\n创造者沉默了。很久很久。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_083_world3_think"},
    {"id":"scene_082_world3_destroy","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你选择了毁灭。\n\n创造者看着你，眼中闪过一丝...\n\n欣慰？\n\n「如你所愿。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_084_world3_ending_destroy"},
    {"id":"scene_082_world3_protect","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"洛恩","dialogue":"「为了所有世界的人！」\n\n你喊道。\n\n「为了艾莉娅，为了 K-7，为了林小满！」\n\n「为了所有...活着的生命！」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_083_world3_unite"},
    {"id":"scene_083_world3_confront","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"「那就来吧。」\n\n创造者举起了手。\n\n纯白的空间开始崩塌，无数记忆碎片向我们涌来。\n\n我感受到了——艾莉娅的勇气，K-7 的疑惑，洛恩的悲伤，林小满的决心。\n\n这些都是我。都是我。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_084_world3_final"},
    {"id":"scene_083_world3_merge","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"创造者开始消散。\n\n他的身体化作无数光点，融入我的体内。\n\n我感觉到了——所有的记忆，所有的情感，所有的痛苦和快乐。\n\n我...成为了完整的存在。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_084_world3_complete"},
    {"id":"scene_083_world3_think","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"创造者陷入了沉思。你选择：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_037_a","text":"【说服】「让他们继续存在吧。」","nextSceneId":"scene_084_world3_persuade","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":15,"wisdom":10},"bonds":{"world1":5,"world2":5,"world3":5,"world4":5}}},{"id":"choice_037_b","text":"【挑战】「你根本没有答案，对吧？」","nextSceneId":"scene_084_world3_challenge","effects":{"stats":{"courage":10,"determination":10},"hiddenStats":{"chaos":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_083_world3_unite","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"所有的羁绊汇聚成力量。\n\n你感受到了...\n\n所有世界的支持。","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_084_world3_power"},
    {"id":"scene_084_world3_final","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"最终的选择时刻。你决定：","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_038_a","text":"【毁灭】「我选择毁灭。」","nextSceneId":"ending_destroyer","effects":{"hiddenStats":{"corruption":30}}},{"id":"choice_038_b","text":"【牺牲】「我选择牺牲自己。」","nextSceneId":"ending_sacrifice","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":20},"hiddenStats":{"corruption":-20}}},{"id":"choice_038_c","text":"【守护】「我选择守护。」","nextSceneId":"ending_guardian","effects":{"stats":{"determination":20,"courage":10},"bonds":{"world1":10,"world2":10,"world3":10,"world4":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_084_world3_complete","worldId":"world3","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"你成为了完整的存在。现在，你选择：","background":"void","characters":[],"choices":[{"id":"choice_039_a","text":"【统治】「我选择统治所有世界。」","nextSceneId":"ending_tyant","effects":{"stats":{"determination":15},"hiddenStats":{"corruption":15,"chaos":10}}},{"id":"choice_039_b","text":"【解放】「我选择让所有世界自由。」","nextSceneId":"ending_liberator","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":15,"compassion":10},"bonds":{"world1":15,"world2":15,"world3":15,"world4":15}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_084_world3_persuade","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"「你说得对。」\n\n创造者说。\n\n「也许...也许我错了。」\n\n「也许生命的意义，就在于它们的短暂和脆弱。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"ending_true_rebirth"},
    {"id":"scene_084_world3_challenge","worldId":"world3","type":"dialogue","speaker":"创造者","dialogue":"创造者愣住了。\n\n然后，他笑了。\n\n「你说得对。」他说，「我没有答案。」\n\n「也许...也许我不该寻找答案。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"ending_true_cycle"},
    {"id":"scene_084_world3_power","worldId":"world3","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"羁绊的力量...\n\n这是最强大的力量。\n\n「我不会输。」","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":"scene_085_world3_climax"},
    {"id":"scene_085_world3_climax","worldId":"world3","type":"ending","speaker":"","title":"第三章结局：神陨","dialogue":"你与创造者展开了最终对决。\n\n神与半神的战斗。\n\n创造与毁灭的碰撞。\n\n结果...由你决定。\n\n【第三章 完】","background":"void","characters":["creator"],"nextSceneId":null}
